        overrideMaxHeight = false,
        customMaxHeightPx = 0,
        addImageText = false,
        imageTextData = {},
      },
      {
        paragraphType = "Text",
        header = "",
        text = "Select the hotkey bar slot with your Building Blocks by pressing the according number key or by using your scroll wheel to move the active slot to the left or right. When the slot is active you will start to see a placeholder object when you aim towards the terrain (limited by maximum building distance). If the placeholder is green you can click to place your Building Block in the world.",
