        paragraphType = "Text",
        header = "",
        text = [[The Drone Miner can be found in your crafting frame. When crafted place it on the foundation you have built next to an ore. It needs to be fully above the foundation and not just partially.

Pro-Tip: You may also right-click a buildable item in your inventory to equip it instantly without the necessity to have it in your hotkey bar - useful for not often required machinery.]],
